'''索娜姆·卡浦爾'''（[[印度語|印度語]]：सोनम कपूर，{{lang-en|Sonam Kapoor}}，{{bd|1985年|6月9日|catIdx=Kapoor, Sonam}}）是印度著名女演員。索娜姆誕生於在一個著名演藝世家，父親[[安尼·卡浦爾|安尼·卡浦爾]]是知名演員。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://zeenews.india.com/entertainment/celebrity-profile/Sonam-Kapoor.htm |title=ZeeNews簡介 |access-date=2014-07-04 |archive-date=2018-08-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180829214532/http://zeenews.india.com/entertainment/celebrity-profile/Sonam-Kapoor.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>母亲苏妮塔是一名[[信德族|信德族]]設計師。<ref>[https://www.cntraveller.in/story/sonam-kapoor-on-her-most-delicious-relationship-yet/ “Sonam Kapoor on her most delicious relationship yet”] {{Wayback|url=https://www.cntraveller.in/story/sonam-kapoor-on-her-most-delicious-relationship-yet/ |date=20210119215147 }}. Conde Nast Traveller India. 04-05-2018.</ref>

雖姓氏相同，但她和印度另一演藝世家[[卡浦爾家族|卡浦爾家族]]並沒有親屬關係。其出道作是電影[[莎華麗雅_(電影)|莎華麗雅]]。

2018年5月8日，她和德里商人安南德·阿胡贾结婚，并跟随丈夫改姓名為索娜姆·卡浦爾-阿胡贾。<ref>[https://www.ndtv.com/entertainment/sonam-kapoor-and-anand-ahujas-wedding-they-are-married-meet-sonam-kapoor-ahuja-1848918 “Sonam Kapoor And Anand Ahuja Are Married. See Wedding Pic”] {{Wayback|url=https://www.ndtv.com/entertainment/sonam-kapoor-and-anand-ahujas-wedding-they-are-married-meet-sonam-kapoor-ahuja-1848918 |date=20200813005829 }}. NDTV. 08-05-2018.</ref>

